<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Thank you – CollectorAnalytics</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: #000;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, sans-serif;
      color: #fff;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .card {
      background: #111;
      border: 1px solid #333;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2rem;
      max-width: 400px;
    }
    h1 { margin: 0 0 1rem; font-size: 1.5rem; }
    p { color: #ccc; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    a {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
      background: #1a5fb4;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    a:hover { background: #3584e4; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1>You're in</h1>
    <p>Thanks for subscribing. You now have access to the members-only area.</p>
    <a href="/members">Go to Members area</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
